data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow home nestled in the heart of historic downtown DeLand. Located in an ideal location just 2.3 miles from Stetson University, this residence offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort.  Step inside to discover a well crafted living room space, perfect for modern family living. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the spacious living area and the well-appointed kitchen. With four generously sized bedrooms, there's ample space for your family or guests.  One of the standout features of this home is its unique lifestyle offering. Surrounded by outdoor activities, you can easily indulge in the beauty of nature, from historic walks in downtown DeLand to exploring nearby parks and recreational areas. For beach enthusiasts, the property's proximity to I-4 ensures quick and hassle-free access to both New Smyrna Beach and Daytona Beach, allowing you to soak up the sun and enjoy the coastal lifestyle. This property truly embodies the best of both worlds: the tranquility of a historic town and the convenience of nearby urban amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful DeLand residence your new home. *Limited Photos as Seller is in process of moving.
